---
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<section class="feature-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Features</h2>
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <Card
      title="Smart Model Routing"
      icon="🧠"
      description="Routes tasks to the optimal AI model based on complexity and cost. Fast models handle simple fixes while expert models tackle deep architectural issues."
    />
    <Card
      title="Keep/Discard Fix Loop"
      icon="🔄"
      description="Automated fix cycles that validate each patch against your test suite. Fixes that fail are discarded and regenerated until a passing solution emerges."
    />
    <Card
      title="Stability Gate"
      icon="🛡️"
      description="Every fix must pass a stability check before reaching your repository. This gate prevents regressions by verifying tests, builds, and lint checks all pass."
    />
    <Card
      title="Semantic Memory"
      icon="💾"
      description="Persists context across sessions so the squad learns from past fixes. This memory helps avoid repeated mistakes and accelerates resolution of similar issues."
    />
    <Card
      title="Multi-Team Support"
      icon="👥"
      description="Multiple engineering teams can operate independently with isolated contexts. Each team gets its own routing preferences, memory, and fix history."
    />
    <Card
      title="A2A Protocol"
      icon="🔗"
      description="Agents communicate using the Agent-to-Agent protocol for coordinated workflows. This enables seamless handoffs between monitoring, investigation, and fix agents."
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .feature-section {
    background: #f0f4f8;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
